{"word":"προσνήχομαι","slug":"προσνήχομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσνήχομαι</b></el> <p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to swim towards</i>, <el>τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:intransitive'>intr.</a> in <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>Act.</a></a> <i>to dash upon</i>, <el>προσένᾱχε θάλασσα</el> <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}